  "texts": [
    "For instance, if a traveler expresses dissatisfaction with a particular recommendation or alters their travel plan, GPT can instantaneously recalibrate and provide alternative suggestions that are better aligned with the traveler's current context and preferences (Wang et al., 2019).",
    "Additionally, personalizing travel encompasses not only catering to practicalities and activities but also understanding and",
    "Qeios, CC-BY 4.0 • Article, March 5, 2024 Qeios ID: UYRUWT • https://doi.org/10.32388/UYRUWT 10/50",
    "aligning recommendations with the traveler's emotional and experiential aspirations.",
    "GPT, with its capacity to understand and generate emotive and contextually relevant text, has the potential to craft communication and recommendations that resonate on a more personal and emotionally engaging level with travelers."
  ]
